OL,3,CThe scientists on global warming's
OL,4,Cfront line in the Arctic circle
OL,6,FITV News' Science Correspondent Martin
OL,7,FStew, Health and Science Producer
OL,8,FPhilip Sime and Camera Operator
OL,9,FBarnaby Green report from Svalbard in
OL,10,Fthe Arctic Circle
OL,12,FThe Arctic is the rapidly melting
OL,13,Ffront line of global warming.
OL,15,FThe island of Spitsbergen in Svalbard,
OL,16,FNorway, is warming around three times
OL,17,Ffaster than most places on our planet.
