OL,3,CThe scientists on global warming's
OL,4,Cfront line in the Arctic circle
OL,6,FUnderstanding how and why it's melting
OL,7,Fso fast could hold the key to
OL,8,Fpreparing the planet for our changing
OL,9,Fclimate.
OL,11,FWe've been invited to join scientists
OL,12,Ffrom the Natural Environment Research
OL,13,FCouncil and the British Antarctic
OL,14,FSurvey at their base in Ny-Alesund.
OL,16,FAt 78.55 degrees north - just a few
OL,17,Fhundred miles from the North Pole - it
OL,18,Fis the world's northernmost settlement.
