OL,3,CThe scientists on global warming's
OL,4,Cfront line in the Arctic circle
OL,6,FTo reach the town requires a flight on
OL,7,Fa twin-turboprop plane from
OL,8,FLongyearbyen, the main settlement on
OL,9,FSpitsbergen.
OL,11,FThe island is roughly the size of
OL,12,FScotland, but fewer than 3,000 people
OL,13,Flive there.
OL,15,FAs we bump through the low cloud, you
OL,16,Fget glimpses of huge glaciers snaking
OL,17,Fbeneath. The island is browner than I
OL,18,Fhad expected.
