OL,3,CThe scientists on global warming's
OL,4,Cfront line in the Arctic circle
OL,6,FAt this time of year, snow and ice
OL,7,Flevels are always at their lowest but
OL,8,Fthings appear to be becoming more
OL,9,Fextreme.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FAfter landing on a gravel runway, we
OL,17,Fhead into the old mining town, which
OL,18,Fis now an international hub for polar
OL,19,Fresearch.
