OL,3,CThe scientists on global warming's
OL,4,Cfront line in the Arctic circle
OL,6,FThere are teams here from 10 different
OL,7,Fcountries ranging to Norway to
OL,8,FGermany, Japan, South Korea and even
OL,9,FChina.
OL,11,FWe meet French scientists Thomas
OL,12,FPoinsot and Celas Marie-Saint. Their
OL,13,Fteam has been releasing weather
OL,14,Fballoons daily since the 1980s.
OL,16,FTheir data has contributed to
OL,17,Frecordings which show average winters
OL,18,Fin Svalbard are 7.7 degrees celcius
OL,19,Fwarmer now than they were 50 years ago.
